data.description: This expansive 4,668 sqft residence boasts tall ceilings that create a grand and spacious atmosphere throughout.   Step inside and be captivated by the elegance of a spiral staircase that adds a touch of sophistication to the home's design.     The heart of the home is the large open kitchen, a culinary haven equipped with modern amenities and perfect for entertaining. With an office both upstairs and downstairs, this home offers versatile spaces for remote work or a private study. Upstairs, indulge in the ultimate entertainment experience with a dedicated theater room and media room, providing the perfect venues for movie nights or watching your favorite sports events.     The large yard provides ample space for outdoor activities, ensuring a perfect blend of indoor and outdoor living.  This property exemplifies the epitome of comfort, style, and functionality, making it an ideal haven for those who appreciate the finer things in life.
